    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nirih</strong> 是一款节奏极快的垂直平台游戏，将闪电般精准的移动与自由落体中的高强度反应相结合。你将以惊人的速度坠入各个关卡，克服具有挑战性的障碍、狭窄的通道和致命的陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在三个独特世界中的 30 个高难度关卡里追猎你的目标，优化你的通关时间，一路冲击全球排行榜的顶端。只有最快、最熟练的玩家才能登上巅峰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你准备好迎接挑战了吗？</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快速游戏体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用 Boss 残留下来的能量来提升你的速度，在关卡中飞驰而过。但务必保持警惕, 当你追踪它们的足迹时，阴险的障碍和致命的陷阱无处不在。只有完美掌握专注与速度的人，才能在坠入未知的过程中存活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战紧张刺激的 Boss 战，追捕你的猎物，并躲避它们致命的攻击和狡猾的陷阱。只有凭借完美的时机和快速的反应，你才能将它们击败。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291700/extras/4d96edf00c7746d2a4fbe7a3953fbb7e.poster.avif?t=1764954170\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291700/extras/4d96edf00c7746d2a4fbe7a3953fbb7e.webm?t=1764954170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>危机四伏的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熟悉各个关卡以及每个世界的特性，并将它们转化为你的优势，不断刷新你的最高分。打破个人最佳时间以解锁新的关卡和外观物品——最终征服全球排行榜的顶端。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291700/extras/1e9c7383e3455cb64da43d44e8df098b.poster.avif?t=1764954170\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291700/extras/1e9c7383e3455cb64da43d44e8df098b.webm?t=1764954170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创造新纪录</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打破各个关卡中的个人最佳成绩，解锁新关卡，并探索更多世界及其挑战。赢得各种外观物品，定制你的猎人，展现你独特的风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291700/extras/19e3da28818897a7db03464f3d8f0e7f.poster.avif?t=1764954170\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291700/extras/19e3da28818897a7db03464f3d8f0e7f.webm?t=1764954170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
